   rymQ(function() {
      RYMchart.initWithState(window.RYMchartDefaultState);
   });


</script></section><section id="page_charts_section_saved_charts" class="page_section page_charts_section ui_section_nav_marker">

         (function() {

            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {
               var regexp = /pwtv=(.*?)(&|$)/g;
               var matches = regexp.exec(purl);
               if ( matches.length >= 2 && matches[1].length > 0 ) {

               function destroyAdhesion(slotName) {
                  console.log(`rym.ads: calling destroySlot on div-gpt-ad-${slotName}`)
                  googletag.destroySlots([window.rym_ad_slot_refs[`div-gpt-ad-${slotName}`]]);

                  el.parentNode.removeChild(el);
               }

         (function() {
            var purl = window.location.href;
            var url = '//ads.pubmatic.com/AdServer/js/pwt/162157/7704';
            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {

            var profileVersionId = '';

               function destroyAdhesion(slotName) {
                  console.log(`rym.ads: calling destroySlot on div-gpt-ad-${slotName}`)
                  googletag.destroySlots([window.rym_ad_slot_refs[`div-gpt-ad-${slotName}`]]);
